  <brief_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Active-controlled, Phase 3 Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Metformin/Atorvastatin Combination Therapy in Subjects With Type II Diabetes and Dyslipidemia</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
