  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Multi-center, Randomized, double-blind, active-controlled, phase 3 trial to evaluate the
      safety and efficacy of Metformin/Atorvastatin in subjects with Type II Diabetes and
      dyslipidemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
